.sidebarmenu UL {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px;
	LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none;
	MARGIN: 0px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 0px;
	WIDTH: 100%;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 0px;
	FONT: 12px;
	font-weight:bold;
	visibility:visible;
	overflow:visible;
	
	PADDING-TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI {
	POSITION: relative;
	overflow:visible;
	
	
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 4px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 4px;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 4px;
	DISPLAY: block;
	COLOR: white;
	
	OVERFLOW:visible;
	TEXT-DECORATION: none;
	PADDING-TOP: 4px;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:link {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
	}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:active {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	COLOR: white
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:hover {
		text-decoration:underline;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI UL {
	POSITION: absolute; WIDTH: 200px; VISIBILITY: hidden; TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu A.subfolderstyle {
	BACKGROUND: url(../right.gif) no-repeat 97% 50%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI {
	FLOAT: left; HEIGHT: 1%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	HEIGHT: 1%
}
', 

', 

//Nested Side Bar Menu (Mar 20th, 09)
//By Dynamic Drive: http://www.dynamicdrive.com/style/

var menuids=["sidebarmenu1"] //Enter id(s) of each Side Bar Mens main UL, separated by commas

function initsidebarmenu(){
for (var i=0; i<menuids.length; i++){
  var ultags=document.getElementById(menuids[i]).getElementsByTagName("ul")
    for (var t=0; t<ultags.length; t++){
    ultags[t].parentNode.getElementsByTagName("a")[0].className+=" subfolderstyle"
  if (ultags[t].parentNode.parentNode.id==menuids[i]) //if this is a first level submenu
   ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t].parentNode.offsetWidth+"px" //dynamically position first level submenus to be width of main menu item
  else //else if this is a sub level submenu (ul)
    ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t-1].getElementsByTagName("a")[0].offsetWidth+"px" //position menu to the right of menu item that activated it
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseover=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="block"
    }
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseout=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="none"
    }
    }
  for (var t=ultags.length-1; t>-1; t--){ //loop through all sub menus again, and use "display:none" to hide menus (to prevent possible page scrollbars
  ultags[t].style.visibility="visible"
  ultags[t].style.display="none"
  }
  }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
window.addEventListener("load", initsidebarmenu, false)
else if (window.attachEvent)
window.attachEvent("onload", initsidebarmenu)

.sidebarmenu UL {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px;
	LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none;
	MARGIN: 0px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 0px;
	WIDTH: 100%;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 0px;
	FONT: 12px;
	font-weight:bold;
	visibility:visible;
	overflow:visible;
	
	PADDING-TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI {
	POSITION: relative;
	overflow:visible;
	
	
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 4px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 4px;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 4px;
	DISPLAY: block;
	COLOR: white;
	
	OVERFLOW:visible;
	TEXT-DECORATION: none;
	PADDING-TOP: 4px;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:link {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
	}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:active {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	COLOR: white
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:hover {
		text-decoration:underline;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI UL {
	POSITION: absolute; WIDTH: 200px; VISIBILITY: hidden; TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu A.subfolderstyle {
	BACKGROUND: url(../right.gif) no-repeat 97% 50%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI {
	FLOAT: left; HEIGHT: 1%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	HEIGHT: 1%
}
', 

', 

//Nested Side Bar Menu (Mar 20th, 09)
//By Dynamic Drive: http://www.dynamicdrive.com/style/

var menuids=["sidebarmenu1"] //Enter id(s) of each Side Bar Mens main UL, separated by commas

function initsidebarmenu(){
for (var i=0; i<menuids.length; i++){
  var ultags=document.getElementById(menuids[i]).getElementsByTagName("ul")
    for (var t=0; t<ultags.length; t++){
    ultags[t].parentNode.getElementsByTagName("a")[0].className+=" subfolderstyle"
  if (ultags[t].parentNode.parentNode.id==menuids[i]) //if this is a first level submenu
   ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t].parentNode.offsetWidth+"px" //dynamically position first level submenus to be width of main menu item
  else //else if this is a sub level submenu (ul)
    ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t-1].getElementsByTagName("a")[0].offsetWidth+"px" //position menu to the right of menu item that activated it
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseover=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="block"
    }
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseout=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="none"
    }
    }
  for (var t=ultags.length-1; t>-1; t--){ //loop through all sub menus again, and use "display:none" to hide menus (to prevent possible page scrollbars
  ultags[t].style.visibility="visible"
  ultags[t].style.display="none"
  }
  }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
window.addEventListener("load", initsidebarmenu, false)
else if (window.attachEvent)
window.attachEvent("onload", initsidebarmenu)

.sidebarmenu UL {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px;
	LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none;
	MARGIN: 0px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 0px;
	WIDTH: 100%;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 0px;
	FONT: 12px;
	font-weight:bold;
	visibility:visible;
	overflow:visible;
	
	PADDING-TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI {
	POSITION: relative;
	overflow:visible;
	
	
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 4px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 4px;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 4px;
	DISPLAY: block;
	COLOR: white;
	
	OVERFLOW:visible;
	TEXT-DECORATION: none;
	PADDING-TOP: 4px;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:link {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
	}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:active {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	COLOR: white
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:hover {
		text-decoration:underline;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI UL {
	POSITION: absolute; WIDTH: 200px; VISIBILITY: hidden; TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu A.subfolderstyle {
	BACKGROUND: url(../right.gif) no-repeat 97% 50%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI {
	FLOAT: left; HEIGHT: 1%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	HEIGHT: 1%
}
', 

', 

//Nested Side Bar Menu (Mar 20th, 09)
//By Dynamic Drive: http://www.dynamicdrive.com/style/

var menuids=["sidebarmenu1"] //Enter id(s) of each Side Bar Mens main UL, separated by commas

function initsidebarmenu(){
for (var i=0; i<menuids.length; i++){
  var ultags=document.getElementById(menuids[i]).getElementsByTagName("ul")
    for (var t=0; t<ultags.length; t++){
    ultags[t].parentNode.getElementsByTagName("a")[0].className+=" subfolderstyle"
  if (ultags[t].parentNode.parentNode.id==menuids[i]) //if this is a first level submenu
   ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t].parentNode.offsetWidth+"px" //dynamically position first level submenus to be width of main menu item
  else //else if this is a sub level submenu (ul)
    ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t-1].getElementsByTagName("a")[0].offsetWidth+"px" //position menu to the right of menu item that activated it
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseover=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="block"
    }
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseout=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="none"
    }
    }
  for (var t=ultags.length-1; t>-1; t--){ //loop through all sub menus again, and use "display:none" to hide menus (to prevent possible page scrollbars
  ultags[t].style.visibility="visible"
  ultags[t].style.display="none"
  }
  }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
window.addEventListener("load", initsidebarmenu, false)
else if (window.attachEvent)
window.attachEvent("onload", initsidebarmenu)

.sidebarmenu UL {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px;
	LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none;
	MARGIN: 0px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 0px;
	WIDTH: 100%;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 0px;
	FONT: 12px;
	font-weight:bold;
	visibility:visible;
	overflow:visible;
	
	PADDING-TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI {
	POSITION: relative;
	overflow:visible;
	
	
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	BORDER-BOTTOM: white 0px solid;
	PADDING-BOTTOM: 4px;
	PADDING-LEFT: 4px;
	PADDING-RIGHT: 4px;
	DISPLAY: block;
	COLOR: white;
	
	OVERFLOW:visible;
	TEXT-DECORATION: none;
	PADDING-TOP: 4px;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:link {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3;
	visibility:visible;
	}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:active {
	BACKGROUND-COLOR: #8098b3
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:visited {
	COLOR: white
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI A:hover {
		text-decoration:underline;
}
.sidebarmenu UL LI UL {
	POSITION: absolute; WIDTH: 200px; VISIBILITY: hidden; TOP: 0px
}
.sidebarmenu A.subfolderstyle {
	BACKGROUND: url(../right.gif) no-repeat 97% 50%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI {
	FLOAT: left; HEIGHT: 1%
}
* HTML .sidebarmenu UL LI A {
	HEIGHT: 1%
}
', 

', 

//Nested Side Bar Menu (Mar 20th, 09)
//By Dynamic Drive: http://www.dynamicdrive.com/style/

var menuids=["sidebarmenu1"] //Enter id(s) of each Side Bar Mens main UL, separated by commas

function initsidebarmenu(){
for (var i=0; i<menuids.length; i++){
  var ultags=document.getElementById(menuids[i]).getElementsByTagName("ul")
    for (var t=0; t<ultags.length; t++){
    ultags[t].parentNode.getElementsByTagName("a")[0].className+=" subfolderstyle"
  if (ultags[t].parentNode.parentNode.id==menuids[i]) //if this is a first level submenu
   ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t].parentNode.offsetWidth+"px" //dynamically position first level submenus to be width of main menu item
  else //else if this is a sub level submenu (ul)
    ultags[t].style.left=ultags[t-1].getElementsByTagName("a")[0].offsetWidth+"px" //position menu to the right of menu item that activated it
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseover=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="block"
    }
    ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseout=function(){
    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display="none"
    }
    }
  for (var t=ultags.length-1; t>-1; t--){ //loop through all sub menus again, and use "display:none" to hide menus (to prevent possible page scrollbars
  ultags[t].style.visibility="visible"
  ultags[t].style.display="none"
  }
  }
}

if (window.addEventListener)
window.addEventListener("load", initsidebarmenu, false)
else if (window.attachEvent)
window.attachEvent("onload", initsidebarmenu)

	menu.init("menu","menuhover");
